fields.name: 1906R
fields.description: The upper of the New Balance 1906 sneakers is made of mesh fabric with faux leather inserts. The rubber sole includes a midsole with ABZORB technology, which absorbs shock and easily regains its shape, and a special insert under the heel that increases elasticity and is highly wear-resistant. This versatile, high-tech model is ready to conquer the city streets and go beyond.

fields.name: Hedgehog 06
fields.description: The North Face Hedgehog 06 sneakers are made of genuine suede and textile. The reinforced toe cap provides additional protection from external influences. Lacing with metal eyelets allows you to adjust the fit to suit your needs. The soft, perforated tongue ensures air circulation. The Vibram sole with a grippy tread minimizes slipping and adds confidence to every step.

fields.name: Dunk Low Retro
fields.description: Designed for basketball players but beloved by street style enthusiasts, the Nike Dunk Low Retro sneakers are back with durable overlays in classic colors. This 80s basketball model features a genuine and synthetic leather upper with perforations on the toe box for active air circulation. Lacing with additional eyelets allows you to adjust the fit. The rubber sole with a grippy tread minimizes slippage and makes every step more confident.

The New Balance 860 sneakers are designed for running and active training. The upper is made of mesh fabric with synthetic leather inserts. The lacing system with additional eyelets allows for a tighter fit. A special N-ERGY insert under the heel absorbs shock. ABZORB technology provides good cushioning. Stability Web technology under the arch of the foot provides comfortable support. The rubber sole is complemented by a grippy tread that minimizes slipping on any surface.

fields.name: Mostro XC GORE-TEX
fields.description:
Mostro comes from the Italian word for monster and is a hybrid model that combines two different styles: spiked sneakers for sprinting from the 60s and surfing shoes from the 80s. This version of the PUMA Mostro XC GORE-TEX sneakers is inspired by the outdoors and active recreation outside the city. GORE-TEX membrane technology protects your feet from moisture. The sole is made of durable and flexible TPU and rubber, complemented by a textured tread for traction.

Translated with DeepL.com (free version)

fields.name: Spizike Low
fields.description:
The Jordan Spizike Low men's sneakers pay tribute to Spike Lee's contribution to the cultural influence of basketball in Hollywood. The pair combines style and technology that complement each other perfectly. The upper is made from a blend of genuine and synthetic leather. The lace lock allows for a tighter fit. Nike Air technology provides enhanced cushioning. The solid rubber outsole creates a secure grip on the surface.

Translated with DeepL.com (free version)

fields.name: Warped Runner
fields.description: Sneakers from New Balance's flagship line  the WRPD Runner model. The most striking detail of this pair is the sole. It combines running technology and retro aesthetics with legendary design. FuelCell technology provides enhanced cushioning and energy return during movement. The textile upper with suede inserts allows your feet to breathe. A soft insole adds comfort. The outsole with tread provides traction.

fields.name: PUMA CA Pro Classic II
fields.description: The PUMA CA Pro Classic II sneakers retain their California vibe. The upper is made of soft genuine leather. Perforations on the toe box actively circulate air. Lacing with additional holes ensures a snug fit. The midsole effectively absorbs shock and provides comfort. The rubber outsole is complemented by a grippy tread.

fields.name: Nike Full Force Low
fields.description: The Nike Full Force Low sneakers take us back to the classic AF1 model with the addition of 80s style and retro stitching, making this pair timeless. The upper is made from a combination of genuine and synthetic leather. The perforated toe box provides additional air circulation. The foam midsole ensures softness and responsiveness with every step. The rubber outsole provides reliable traction on any surface.

fields.name: Speedcat Leather
fields.description: The iconic PUMA Speedcat Leather model, inspired by Formula 1 racing. The upper is made of genuine leather. The IMEVA sole provides excellent cushioning, adding softness and comfort with every step. The rubber outsole with tread minimizes slippage and adds confidence on any surface.

fields.name: Intimidation Low
fields.description: The adidas Intimidation Low sneakers are a pair with a unique and dynamic design from the basketball archives of the 90s. The upper is made of textile with a frame of durable materials. Additional eyelets on the laces allow you to adjust the fit. adiPRENE technology protects your feet from stress and provides enhanced cushioning. The grippy tread on the rubber sole adds confidence to every step.

fields.name: Zoom Vomero 5
fields.description: The upper of the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 sneakers is made of mesh fabric with durable and flexible PU inserts for extra foot support. Zoom Air cushioning ensures a light and confident stride. The rubber sole is complemented by a pronounced tread pattern that provides reliable traction.

fields.name: Morphic Retro
fields.description: A true retro runner with a modern twist from PUMA. The Morphic Retro is made partly from recycled materials. Mesh inserts allow for good airflow. Multiple lace holes allow you to adjust the fit. The layered upper is complemented by a cushioned sole with a grippy outsole.
